snippet.title: Force Of Light Entertainment
snippet.description: Join Sisters Michelle and Natalie as they discuss/review movies/tv, rumors and give commentary on current events in the world of entertainment! We hope to foster a positive community where people can respectfully express their opinions about all things in the world of entertainment. Although we take a positive approach our reviews/thoughts are always honest. Join this community, and let's talk some entertainment!
